Class Intersected

java.lang.Object
dev.kkorolyov.pancake.core.component.event.Intersected

dev.kkorolyov.pancake.platform.entity.Component
public final class Intersected extends Object implements dev.kkorolyov.pancake.platform.entity.Component
Notes that an intersection between entities occurred. Each mutually-intersecting entity is provided the same instance of this component.
